docs.lead_paragraph: " The statement that Mr. John S. Thrasher, editor of the 'Faro Industrial', at Havana, has been thrown into prison by the Government, seems to be confirmed. The charges against him have not yet been promulgated. Mr. Thrasher is a young man, a native of Portland, Mo., and has resided in Havana, whither he originally went for his health, about fifteen years ago.
